OL,3,CCommuter says the reintroduction of
OL,4,Cpeak rail fares is 'extremely
OL,5,Cfrustrating'
OL,7,FA Borders commuter who has been forced
OL,8,Fto move back in with her parents due
OL,9,Fto rising costs, has described the
OL,10,Freintroduction of peak rail fares as
OL,11,F'extremely frustrating'.
OL,13,FKate Ferguson, who commutes into
OL,14,FEdinburgh, moved back in with her
OL,15,Fparents due to rent prices in the city
OL,16,Fbeing unaffordable.
