OL,3,CCommuter says the reintroduction of
OL,4,Cpeak rail fares is 'extremely
OL,5,Cfrustrating'
OL,7,FShe said: "Now I have to commute to
OL,8,Fwork in order to get there so that I
OL,9,Fcan save up and hopefully get a place
OL,10,Fout in Edinburgh. A round trip will be
OL,11,Fabout 30 miles and getting to
OL,12,FEdinburgh then takes another hour,
OL,13,Fwhich with the costs of that is about
OL,14,F#350 a month.
OL,16,F"With the prices changing, it means I
OL,17,Fwork from home a lot more instead of
OL,18,Fgoing into the office, because my
OL,19,Fultimate goal is to save."
