OL,3,CCommuter says the reintroduction of
OL,4,Cpeak rail fares is 'extremely
OL,5,Cfrustrating'
OL,7,FKate is saving up so she can move back
OL,8,Fto Edinburgh, but with the pilot
OL,9,Fscheme ending, it's kicked back her
OL,10,Fsaving plan.
OL,12,FShe said: "A good four or five months
OL,13,Fit's going to delay my savings by,
OL,14,Fwhich is huge. Then you have other
OL,15,Ffactors in life which hinder your
OL,16,Fsavings and the way that the economy
OL,17,Fis going. This is just going to add on
OL,18,Fto another obstacle.
