OL,3,CCommuter says the reintroduction of
OL,4,Cpeak rail fares is 'extremely
OL,5,Cfrustrating'
OL,7,F"It's extremely frustrating, because
OL,8,Fthe whole reason to come back down and
OL,9,Fto commute was to save. Now with this
OL,10,Fmassive addition, it just makes that
OL,11,Fsaving go further away."
OL,13,FScotland's First Minister John Swinney
OL,14,Fhas insisted the target to cut car
OL,15,Fusage by the end of this decade can
OL,16,Fstill be met despite his government
OL,17,Faxing a trial scheme for cut-price
OL,18,Frail fares. The initiative will end on
OL,19,F27 September 2024.
