OL,3,CCommuter says the reintroduction of
OL,4,Cpeak rail fares is 'extremely
OL,5,Cfrustrating'
OL,7,FCritics have warned that the end of
OL,8,Fthe year-long trial will force more
OL,9,Fcommuters onto the roads. The scheme
OL,10,Fabolished peak rate tickets, enabling
OL,11,Fpassengers to pay-off peak fares
OL,12,Fregardless of the time of travel.
OL,14,FIt was introduced in a bid to reduce
OL,15,F20% of kilometres travelled by car by
OL,16,F2030.
OL,18,FMr Swinney believes the #40m bill per
OL,19,Fyear for the scheme meant it was "not
OL,20,Fjustified to continue the pilot at
OL,21,Fthat cost."
