OL,3,CCommuter says the reintroduction of
OL,4,Cpeak rail fares is 'extremely
OL,5,Cfrustrating'
OL,7,FExpert advisers believe it would be
OL,8,F"extraordinarily difficult" for the
OL,9,Freducing emissions target to be met,
OL,10,Fsaid at the Climate Change Committee
OL,11,Fin April 2024.
OL,13,FMarion Short, Chair of Campaign for
OL,14,FBorders Rail, believes it is the wrong
OL,15,Fthing to do.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
