OL,3,CCommuter says the reintroduction of
OL,4,Cpeak rail fares is 'extremely
OL,5,Cfrustrating'
OL,7,FShe said: "It's a retrograde step and
OL,8,FI think they should be encouraging
OL,9,Fpeople to use the train more.
OL,10,FParticularly in line with the fact
OL,11,Fthat the Scottish Government have
OL,12,Ftargets to meet in terms of climate
OL,13,Fcontrol.
OL,15,F"Commuters are now happily working
OL,16,Ffrom home. If they introduce peak
OL,17,Ftravel again, that's going to affect
OL,18,Fthis group of people considerably.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
