OL,3,CCommuter says the reintroduction of
OL,4,Cpeak rail fares is 'extremely
OL,5,Cfrustrating'
OL,7,F"Does it mean they are going to lose
OL,8,Fmore passengers again as opposed to
OL,9,Fcreating more passenger numbers?"
OL,11,FBorders MSP Christine Grahame, SNP
OL,13,FWhen questioned whether the target
OL,14,Fcould be met, First Minister Swinney
OL,15,Fsaid: "Yes, I think it can."
OL,17,FHe added this "obviously requires
OL,18,Fchanges in behaviour from members of
OL,19,Fthe public" - saying achieving this
OL,20,Fwas "not focused simply on one
OL,21,Fparticular policy intervention".
