OL,3,CCommuter says the reintroduction of
OL,4,Cpeak rail fares is 'extremely
OL,5,Cfrustrating'
OL,7,FHe added that while the peak fares
OL,8,Fpilot had "demonstrated a limited
OL,9,Famount of success", and had boosted
OL,10,Frail passenger numbers to "some
OL,11,Fextent", it had "not delivered the
OL,12,Fmodal shift we had hoped would be the
OL,13,Fcase".
OL,15,FWith the scheme requiring "significant
OL,16,Famounts of public investment to make
OL,17,Fit work" and the Scottish Government
OL,18,F"operating under significant financial
OL,19,Fconstraint", Mr Swinney said it had
OL,20,Fnot been possible to continue with it.
